1. Open Outlook
2. Click "File"
3. Click "Account Settings" twice
4. Once the new window pops up, Click on your email while in the Email tab
5. Click on "Change"
6. On the next window, select "More Settings" in the lower right hand corner
7. On the pop up go to the "Advanced" Tab
8. Click "Add"
9. Type or paste in the mailbox name
10. Click "OK" on the Add Mailbox and Microsoft Exchange windows
11. Click "Next" on the Change Account window
12. Click "Finish"​
